import React from 'react';
import { ProSidebar, Menu, MenuItem, SubMenu , SidebarHeader , SidebarContent , SidebarFooter } from 'react-pro-sidebar';
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
import { faTable , faPlusSquare , faAddressBook, faAtom, faTachometerAlt, faGlobe, faHome, faChalkboard, faAd, faChartBar, faCheckSquare, faRecycle } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'

const Sidebar = ({activemenu, submenu}) => {
  return (
    <ProSidebar  breakPoint={'md'}> 
     <SidebarContent>
    <Menu iconShape="round">

      <MenuItem 
        active={activemenu === 'DASHBOARD'} 
        icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTachometerAlt} />}>
          Dashboard<Link to="/dashboard" />
      </MenuItem>

<SubMenu  defaultOpen={activemenu === 'STUDENT'} title="Student" icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faAddressBook} />}>
      <MenuItem 
            active={submenu === 'STUDENT_TB_LIST'} >
            Manage Students<Link to="/student/student_tb_list" />
        </MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>

      <SubMenu title="Tags" defaultOpen={activemenu==='TAGS'} icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faAd}/>}>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_TAGS'}>Manage Tags<Link to="/tags/AddTags"/></MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>

      
      <SubMenu  defaultOpen={activemenu === 'WORKING_DAYS'} title="Working Days" icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTable} />}>
        <MenuItem 
            active={submenu === 'DAYS_LIST'} >
            Manage Working Day<Link to="/workingdays/list" />
        </MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_WORKING_DAYS'}>
          Add Working Days<Link to="/workingdays/add" />
        </MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>



      <SubMenu active={activemenu === 'LECTURER'}  title="Lecturers" icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faAddressBook} />}>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'OVERVIEW_LECTURER'}><Link to="/lecturer/overview" />Manage Lecture</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_LECTURER'}>Add Lecturer <Link to="/lecturer/add" /></MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>

      <SubMenu title="Subjects" active={activemenu === 'SUBJECT'} icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faAtom} />}>
      <MenuItem active={submenu === 'OVERVIEW_SUBJECT'}>Manage Subject<Link to="/subject/overview" /></MenuItem>
      <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_SUBJECT'}>Add Subject <Link to="/subject/add" /></MenuItem>

      </SubMenu>


      
      <SubMenu title="Buildings" defaultOpen={activemenu === 'BUILDINGS'} icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faHome}/>}>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'BUILDINGS_LIST'}>Manage Buildings <Link to="/locations/buildings/list"/></MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_BUILDING'}>Add Building<Link to="/locations/buildings/add"/></MenuItem> 
      </SubMenu>

      <SubMenu title="Rooms" defaultOpen={activemenu==='ROOMS'} icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faChalkboard}/>}>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ROOMS_LIST'}>Manage Rooms <Link to="/locations/rooms/list"/></MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'ADD_ROOM'}>Add Room<Link to="/locations/rooms/add"/></MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>

      <SubMenu title="Statistics" defaultOpen={activemenu==='STATISTICS'} icon={<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faChartBar}/>}>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'STUDENT_STAT'}>Students<Link to="/stats/stu"/></MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'LEC_STAT'}>Lecturers<Link to="/stats/lec"/></MenuItem>
        <MenuItem active={submenu === 'SUB_STAT'}>Subject<Link to="/stats/sub"/></MenuItem>
      </SubMenu>


    </Menu>
    </SidebarContent>
  </ProSidebar>
  );
}

export default Sidebar;
